1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
Did you know octopuses can rewrite their own genetic messages?

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:09,200
They can perform A-to-I RNA editing, transforming their neural transcripts on the fly.

3
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:12,000
But hold on, this isn't DNA rewriting!

4
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:17,200
Research from scientists like Rosenthal and Liscovitch-Brauer shows these edits enhance their adaptability.

5
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:22,800
This RNA editing helps octopuses thrive in different environments, reacting to challenges in real-time.

6
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:26,000
It’s an evolutionary trade-off, balancing complexity with survival.

7
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:26,800
Incredible, right?

8
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:28,800
Curious about more weird science?

